{"id": 2975, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常聊天时，你都用过哪些“自带捧哏”的半括号句式？", "description": "用了半括号之后感觉自己也瞬间变萌了呢（并没有。（题图来自：iStock ©️ VictoriaBar）", "record_count": 0, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190531140609Y30lUQZMXNhwxPb6.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5867, "title": "日常聊天时，你都用过哪些“自带捧哏”的半括号句式？", "content": "日常聊天时，你都用过哪些“自带捧哏”的半括号句式？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 345778, "content": "缓和气氛型：其实我觉得不好看（超小声", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174107BJIX6be2Gv4PMfyq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345779, "content": "展开讲讲型：哈哈哈哈（没错就是我了", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174230yVSFKsfErNvqUthz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345780, "content": "自带现场型：感到得意（让我叉会儿腰哼", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174244O90JaAK6mR4nw5uP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345781, "content": "自我挽尊型：对啊我很懒（也不是，就是不想起床", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174327WLc1nIypCbH63VvU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345782, "content": "解释原因型：今天没出门（因为昨天晚上发烧了", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174357DVUEP6KcxLgk9hu7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345783, "content": "吐槽自黑型：今天也是努力工作的一天呢（并没有", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174420G7JkFhcgU35CpHys.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345785, "content": "纯粹卖萌型：我真的生气了！（哄不好的那种", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174728Co1BfitAyOhU2WYV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345784, "content": "都不是，我是全括号党（全括号赛高）", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174440uM7Ve8sdf1JTl9Lt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 345786, "content": "都不是，我是方括号党【还是方括号最好使", "image": "img/option/option/20190531174544DI0KMRgand8yTeWt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}